These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani, mexican, argentine
1. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
2. the argentine is between the indonesian and the pakistani##2
3. the argentine is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | argentine | pakistani | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, strawberry, cauliflower, spinach
1. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating strawberry is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | strawberry | corn | spinach | cauliflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, sports, epic, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
2. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching sports movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | comedy | epic | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, handball, lacrosse, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | handball | tennis | water-polo | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skiing, climbing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | badminton | weightlifting | climbing | skiing |

