.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, japanese, dutch, australian
1. the japanese is on the far right##1
2. the japanese is on the left or right of the australian##3
3. the dutch is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | dutch | egyptian | australian | japanese |

