1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | helicopter | snowmobile | motorbike | skateboard |

