3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
4. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | cricket | basketball | skateboarding | golf |

