.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, cucumber, tomato, grapes
1. the person eating cucumber is the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
3. the person eating tomato is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | tomato | grapes | cucumber | nectarine |

